Filtering: 

Alt+Down Arrow+S – Sort A to Z
Alt+Down Arrow+O – Sort Z to A
Alt+Down Arrow+T – Sort by Color sub menu
Alt+Down Arrow+I – Filter by Color sub menu
Alt+Down Arrow+F – Text or Date Filter sub menu

Ctrl+Shift+L -- toggle row filter

Alt+Down Arrow+F+E+Enter -- filter for blanks cells in the column

Alt+A+C -- clear all the filters in the current filtered range

Alt+Down+Arrow+E -- open the filter drop down menu and jump directly to the search box
